{
  "texts": [
    "They also mostly fail to do unit conversions, e.g.",
    "from meters to centimeters or from kilometers per hour to meters per second.",
    "Astonishingly, ChatGPT is able to do the latter, but unable to correctly perform the former, although it recognizes that it has to do a conversion.Regarding scale, there was no clear tendency.",
    "Although larger models performed better in general (e.g.",
    "LLaMA 13b was 5.5% absolute better than LLaMA 7b), both LLaMA and OPT 30b models performed worse than the smaller models."
  ]
}